==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Obtected
<hw>Ob*tect"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>obtectus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>obtegere</ets> to cover over.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>Covered; protected.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Covered with a hard chitinous
case, as the pupa of certain flies; also called
<altname>obtect</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Obtemper</ent>⟦br⟧
